{"title":"疫情下的颐和园","date":"2020-03-20T10:56:25.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年3月20日","L":"2020/03/20","MM-DD":"03-20"},"thumbnail":"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/shi-qi-kong-qiao.jpg","link":"2020/03/20/travel/yhy","comments":true,"tags":["北京","旅游","疫情"],"categories":["杂记"],"updated":"2020-04-12T04:16:35.273Z","content":"<p>疫情期间的颐和园，人烟稀少，却是风光无限，沉淀出了时光的痕迹。<br>择一日，春光曼妙，风和日丽，漫步园中，岁月静好。</p>\n<h2 id=\"园内风景\">园内风景<a href=\"#园内风景\" title=\"园内风景\"></a></h2><p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/shi-qi-kong-qiao.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"十七孔桥\"><br>十七孔桥</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc0428.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"远观玉峰塔\"><br>远观玉峰塔</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc0448.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"清净的湖面\"><br>清净的湖面，风景美不胜收</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc0460.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"盛开的山桃花\"><br>盛开的山桃花</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc0463.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"远眺佛香阁\"><br>远眺佛香阁</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc0465.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"再现十七孔桥\"><br>再现十七孔桥</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc04752.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"零星的观景人\"><br>零星的观景人</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blogimg-1254014761.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/2020/03/20/dsc0482.jpg\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"昔日吵闹的长廊\"><br>昔日吵闹的长廊</p>\n<p>阳春三月，昔日人流如织，如今….</p>\n<p>没有游船，只有野鸭、黑天鹅;<br>没有商店，没有泡面、火腿;</p>\n<p>人烟稀少，却是风光无限。</p>\n<p>希望疫情早点结束…</p>\n<h2 id=\"入园攻略\">入园攻略<a href=\"#入园攻略\" title=\"入园攻略\"></a></h2><ol><li>提前一天“颐和园”官方微信公众号进行预约购票，可预约上午、下午两个时段，不预约不能进。</li><li>第二天直接刷身份证入园（一定要带身份证！！）</li><li>疫情期间只有新建宫门开放，其他都是关闭的。开车前往的旁边有6-7号停车场，方便停车。</li></ol>","prev":{"title":"一条SQL查询语句是如何执行的","link":"2020/03/20/mysql/select-run"},"plink":"https://snailscoder.com/2020/03/20/travel/yhy/","reward":true,"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"https://snailscoder.com/2020/03/20/travel/yhy/\" title=\"疫情下的颐和园\">https://snailscoder.com/2020/03/20/travel/yhy/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}